    <description><![CDATA[&lt;div class=&quot;okr-block-clipboard&quot; data-okr=&quot;%7B%22okrDelta%22%3A%5B%7B%22lineType%22%3A%22text%22%2C%22lineOptions%22%3A%7B%7D%2C%22lineContent%22%3A%5B%7B%22opType%22%3A%22text%22%2C%22options%22%3A%7B%22text%22%3A%22About%20OKEx%3A%22%2C%22bold%22%3Atrue%7D%7D%5D%7D%2C%7B%22lineType%22%3A%22text%22%2C%22lineOptions%22%3A%7B%7D%2C%22lineContent%22%3A%5B%7B%22opType%22%3A%22text%22%2C%22options%22%3A%7B%22text%22%3A%22OKEx%20is%20a%20world-leading%20digital%20asset%20trading%20platform%2C%20providing%20advanced%20financial%20services%20to%20traders%20globally%20by%20using%20blockchain%20technology.%22%7D%7D%5D%7D%2C%7B%22lineType%22%3A%22text%22%2C%22lineOptions%22%3A%7B%7D%2C%22lineContent%22%3A%5B%7B%22opType%22%3A%22text%22%2C%22options%22%3A%7B%22text%22%3A%22OKEx%20provides%20hundreds%20of%20token%20%26%20futures%20trading%20pairs%20to%20help%20traders%20to%20optimize%20their%20strategy.%20We%20are%20also%20one%20of%20the%20top%20digital%20asset%20trading%20platforms%20by%20trading%20volume%2C%20serving%20millions%20of%20users%20in%20over%20100%20countries.%20OKEx%20derivatives%20remains%20a%20top-notch%20venue%20globally%20and%20has%20a%20daily%20volume%20of%20approximately%20%2410%20billion%20and%20is%20widely%20recognized%20as%20the%20golden%20standard%20in%20the%20industry.%20We%20believe%20the%20blockchain%20technology%20will%20eliminate%20barriers%20to%20transactions%2C%20increase%20the%20efficiency%20of%20transactions%20across%20society%2C%20and%20eventually%20have%20a%20significant%20impact%20on%20the%20global%20economy.%20We%20strive%20to%20make%20innovative%20achievements%20that%20change%20the%20world%20and%20never%20stop%20to%20improve%20on%20our%20customer%20experience.%22%7D%7D%5D%7D%2C%7B%22lineType%22%3A%22text%22%2C%22lineOptions%22%3A%7B%7D%2C%22lineContent%22%3A%5B%5D%7D%2C%7B%22lineType%22%3A%22text%22%2C%22lineOptions%22%3A%7B%7D%2C%22lineContent%22%3A%5B%7B%22opType%22%3A%22text%22%2C%22options%22%